						               													<description>La torre degli incantesimi is a roll and move and dexterity game, for 2-4 little magicians.&amp;#10;Each player tries to make his magic potion collecting 4 different ingredients. During his round, a player rolls and moves his magician and does one of the following action according to the space he lands:&amp;#10;- using his dragon, take a small ball and put it inside the tower in the middle of the board. The ball will exit from the tower and land in a bridge: it will be transormed in one ingredient according to the symbol in the bridge.&amp;#10;- take the ingredients from a bridge.&amp;#10;- put a beam inside the tower: it can influence where the ball will exit.&amp;#10;- draw a magic card: for example it could allow the player to take an ingredient for free.&amp;#10;- reroll the dice.&amp;#10;The first player who finishes his potion wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
